  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-style:normal;margin-right:16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);margin-left:16px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"A close-up look at Groq's LPU chip\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100029354\" data-ratio=\"0.533203125\" data-w=\"1024\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0aca3485&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FZ300vPwLQknp2Kmsax4ia6PjK13uqUKoN1p1m21PS2jAAqNqUpRlMWRJ7zfMwk38ZbscnNlWXMy2agk0icKTLuFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></em></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-style:normal;margin-right:16px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);margin-left:16px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;\"><em><span style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><span leaf=\"\">图片来源：</span><font face=\"宋体\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;text-size-adjust:inherit;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-style:italic;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.3);text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;text-align:left;\">Groq</span></font></font></span></em></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">英伟达公司已与人工智能初创公司</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">达成一项批准上市许可</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">/</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">注册协议，进一步深化其对&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">热潮相关企业的投资，并获得了将一项新型技术整合至其产品中的权利。</span></font></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">这家全球市值最高的上市公司已支付使用</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">技术的授权费用，并将把其芯片设计整合到未来产品中。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">两家公司表示，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">的部分高管将离职加入英伟达，以协助此项整合工作。</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">在其官网周三发布的声明中称，公司将保持独立运营，并任命新的首席执行官。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">英伟达的技术已在数据中心领域占据主导地位，而这些数据中心正是支撑</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">软件与服务所需新型计算能力爆发的核心。其现有产品的广泛普及已使英伟达成为芯片行业当之无愧的资本最雄厚企业，该公司表示将利用部分资金推动人工智能在整个经济领域中的普及应用。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">是&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Alphabet&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">旗下的谷歌等正在开发自己&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">芯片以与英伟达竞争的初创公司和企业之一。这家成立于&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">2016&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">年的初创公司在&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">9&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">月以&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">69&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元投后估值融资&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">7.5&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">当时，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">表示将利用这笔资金扩大其数据中心容量。该公司在声明中表示，其提供外包计算的数据中心业务将继续运营。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">首席执行官乔纳森·罗斯是前谷歌芯片高管，曾帮助启动该公司的张量处理单元（</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">TPU</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">），该处理器为&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">工作负载提供动力。</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">在声明中表示，作为交易的一部分，他和其他高管将加入英伟达，</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">\"</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">以帮助推进并扩大授权技术的规模</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">\"</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Groq&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">的低延迟芯片对输入反应极其迅速，将为英伟达的产品增添新功能并开辟新的市场领域。在首席执行官黄仁勋的领导下，这家芯片制造商已推出海量新产品，旨在巩固市场地位并加速企业应用人工智能软件的进程。公司目前除完整计算机系统外，还销售网络设备、软件及服务。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">此项技术许可协议在某些方面类似于</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Meta&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">与数据标注初创公司&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">Scale AI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">达成的合作关系——科技巨头向小规模企业进行大规模投资，获取技术授权并聘用其首席执行官。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">英伟达持续投资于人工智能基础设施生态系统的各家企业，并试图在模型推理市场保持显著优势</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">——即运行已开发完成的人工智能模型。公司领导层已承诺投入数百亿美元支持各类项目，旨在推动整体人工智能行业发展。英伟达同意向&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">OpenAI&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">投资高达&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">1000&nbsp;</span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">亿美元，甚至收购了昔日竞争对手英特尔公司的部分股权。</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\">通过将新型设计融入产品体系，英伟达展现出保持技术弹性与创新能力的决心。在当前行业竞相加速部署计算产能之际，谷歌、微软和亚马逊等科技巨头的自研芯片进展迅猛，英伟达此举旨在稳固核心客户与新兴用户对其技术路线的关注。</span></font></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font face=\"宋体\"></font></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;outline: 0px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__16\">参考资料：</span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-style:italic;\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-24/nvidia-reaches-licensing-deal-with-chip-startup-groq?srnd=phx-technology\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-12-24/nvidia-reaches-licensing-deal-with-chip-startup-groq?srnd=phx-technology</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "英伟达通过技术授权和高管加盟的方式与 AI 芯片初创公司 Groq 达成合作，以整合其低延迟芯片设计，强化在 AI 推理市场的领导地位。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "英伟达通过技术授权和高管加盟的方式与 AI 芯片初创公司 Groq 达成合作，以整合其低延迟芯片设计，强化在 AI 推理市场的领导地位。",
  "summary": "英伟达公司与 AI 初创公司 Groq 达成技术授权协议，将支付费用并将 Groq 的低延迟芯片设计整合到其未来的产品中。作为合作的一部分，Groq 的部分高管，包括前谷歌 TPU 高管、现任 Groq CEO 乔纳森·罗斯将加入英伟达，协助技术整合。尽管如此，Groq 将保持独立运营，并任命新的 CEO。此举显示英伟达旨在通过引入 Groq 的低延迟技术，在 AI 推理市场保持领先地位，应对谷歌、微软和亚马逊等科技巨头在自研芯片方面的竞争。",
